00:19:32,320 --> 00:19:35,570
That's the expected
value of a gamble.

445
00:19:35,570 --> 00:19:38,210
And the profit maximizing thing
to do would be to take

446
00:19:38,210 --> 00:19:42,200
gambles of expected values
of greater than zero.

447
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:45,460
The expected value is
the summation of the

448
00:19:45,460 --> 00:19:47,480
value of that gamble.

449
00:19:47,480 --> 00:19:54,170
This gamble has an expected
